Text: "It\u2019s been 4 years now ! I remember , it was December and I was already\
  \ kicking for 8 hrs to the base camp Fitzroy :) was kind of mix of snow and crazy\
  \ wind and I was sooo hungry cuz I am vegan and it was not easy to get something\
  \ to eat beside meet and empanada which was with chees ! \nAnyways I remember when\
  \ I got up there ( these was a kind of laguna something like that , I slept for\
  \ 2 hrs just on a stone . I thought I will never make it back :D hahahahaha and\
  \ that was the best nap I ever had in my life ."
